text: Western style seafood served here is yummy. It shares a location together with other trendy and upmarket food stalls, sort of like a high class coffee shop with trendy decor.  So the prices are a little steeper. Not air-conditioned though they have many fans placed all around.
Pretty good sea food, in a coffee shop that has other good food too!
waited quite long for the plate of seabass, which came cold, and in fillet although it's supposed to be a whole fish
Love their white bait mac n cheese. Generous serving
